            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Cue Mode — Turn a note's sections into full-screen cue cards you swipe through during recordings and calls</li>
                    <li>Sections — Split any note into sections and jump straight to one with ⌘1 through ⌘9</li>
